Package: gClustPath
Type: Package
Title: Clustering and pathway analysis using gamma distributions
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Anooj",
             family = "Arkatkar",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "arkatkar@msu.edu"))
Description: Clustering and pathway analysis of omics data is performed by
    the use of a gamma distributed affinity/dissimilarity measure.
    This package assumes null inter-cluster correlations and forms 
    pathways that minimize any null linking correlations between
    elements.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
